content_segments.text: This GDMI filter housing configuration is for your rooftop project. The system is exposed to high humidity and outdoor condensation.

The current configuration is blocked. GDMI housings use bolted construction, which does not meet the leakage class and hygiene requirements for outdoor environments. Outdoor installation also causes condensation on non-insulated metal surfaces. Double-wall insulated housing is required to maintain the surface above the dew point.

Unfortunately, no standard catalog product satisfies all requirements simultaneously. A solution would need to be rated for outdoor installation and have a double-wall insulated housing. I recommend contacting our Custom Engineering or Technical Support team with these specific technical requirements.
